<noinclude>
==Documentation==
Closes the /Images subpage layout opened by <code><nowiki>{{ImagesPage}}</nowiki></code>.

Place this at the end of image gallery content.

===Usage===
<pre>
{{ImagesPage}}

== Screenshots ==
<gb-gallery>
0/628/267079-some-image.jpg | Optional caption
</gb-gallery>

{{ImagesPageEnd}}
</pre>

===Structure===
This template closes the following divs opened by <code><nowiki>{{ImagesPage}}</nowiki></code>:
* <code>.gb-{type}-wiki-content</code>
* <code>.gb-{type}-main .gb-images-main</code>
* <code>.gb-{type}-content .gb-images-content</code>
</noinclude><includeonly>{{#invoke:ImagesPage|close}}</includeonly>
